{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_51_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 二日目のボーナスタイム",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～……よく寝た～\nあれっ！？　どうして酒瓶が転がってるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I slept great~.\nHuh?! Why are there sake bottles lying around?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "んん……何？　朝からうるさいわね\n昨晩、貴方達で空けたんでしょう。私は知らないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… What is it? it is noisy in the morning.\nYou two emptied them last night‚ right? I don’t know anything about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、二人とも。……もしかして昨日のこと\n何も覚えてないの？　お酒の味も？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ you two. …Don’t tell me you don’t\nremember anything? Not even the taste of the sake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "二人からプレゼントにお酒をもらったのは覚えてるわ\n味は、うーん辛口？　いや甘口だったかも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember you two giving me sake as a present.\nThe taste… hmm‚ was it dry? Or maybe sweet…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.2333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に覚えてないの！？\n超高級日本酒セットだったのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really don’t remember?!\nIt was a super high-end sake set!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、すっごく美味しかったから\nこんなに酔っ払ったのかな～なんて……遙子大失敗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ well‚ I guess I got carried away‚\nbecause it was really delicious … Haruko‚ big mistake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく呆れるわね。こんな大人にならないよう\n今からリズノワのメンバーにも言っておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m speechless. I have to warn the LizNoir members\nnot to become adults like this from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "二日酔いはどうなの？\n私は少し残ってるけど、今日の活動に支障はないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How’s your hangover?\nI still have a bit‚ but it won’t affect my activities today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私も全然大丈夫ですよ\n一応、二人とも無理はしないようにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m totally fine.\nMake sure you don’t push yourselves‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　こんなに飲んだのに！？\n莉央さんって実は酒豪なの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?! Even after drinking that much?!\nRio-san‚ are you actually a heavy drinker?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1333277385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないでしょ\n貴方達の介抱で自分が酔うどころじゃなかったわよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be ridiculous.\nI was too busy taking care of you two to even think about getting drunk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.1333277385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあ二日酔いも、これから行く\n温泉に浸かれば、吹き飛んじゃうと思うし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W‚ well‚ I’m sure our hangovers\nwill be gone once we soak in the hot spring!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9666544597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "温泉？　そんな話してたかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hot spring? Did we talk about that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9666544597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、言ってなかった？　この近くに\n人が全く来ない穴場の秘湯があるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Didn’t I tell you? There’s this secret hot spring nearby\nthat no one knows about!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4333211263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.0333211263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "今日はそこに寄ってから\n東京に帰るスケジュールになってまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s schedule includes a stop there\nbefore we head back to Tokyo~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.899987793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.0333211263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "撮影も入らないのよね？\nそれなら、ゆっくり出来そうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not filming there‚ right?\nIf so‚ we can relax and enjoy ourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333211263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.699987793
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。大人組だけのボーナスタイムよ\n本当にいい所だから、二人も気に入ると思うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. Bonus time just for us grown-ups!\nIt’s a really great place‚ so I’m sure you’ll both love it!",
        "id": ""
      },
