    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "キャンプ場から意外と近いのね\n昨日と比べて、あっさり着いたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s surprisingly close to the campsite.\nWe got here much faster compared to yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4333134969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁー、気持ちいい\nお湯もしっとりしてて、肌に良さそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ this feels so good.\nThis water is so moist‚ it seems good for the skincare.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0333165486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.6333134968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "この温泉、美肌効果があるみたいなの\nちょっとの間だけど、ゆっくりしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard this hot spring has beautifying effects.\nAlthough it's just a moment‚ let’s relax and enjoy it.",
        "id": ""
