      "text": "ええ、悪くなかったわ。貴方が秘湯って言うから\n変な所に連れてかれるのかと思ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it wasn’t bad. When you said “secret hot spring‚”\nI thought you were going to take us somewhere weird.",
